        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>Collection includes eighty postcards. Dated cards range from 1906 through 1995, but many cards are not dated. Cards depict various subjects including campus views, campus buildings, football, Corps of Cadets, and Blacksburg views. Some of the postcards are postmarked and addressed to recipients, while some are blank.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <arrangement id="ref18">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>This collection is arranged chronologically by decade.</p>
        </arrangement>
